    "DDI: Ticagrelor / Phenytoin a.",
    "Clinical importance/relevance: Important b.",
    "Rationale: Phenytoin induces hepatic metabolism of ticagrelor through CYP3A4, resulting in subtherapeutic plasma levels of ticagrelor and increasing risk of clinical failure. 14.",
